intensely about something it could be a
deep grief maybe due to the loss of a
dear and near one the word profound
basically means something that is
characterized or described by intensity
or depth when you feel or experience
something very strongly or in an extreme
manner you actually have a profound
experience profound means to emphasize
something that is very intense or
something that has a strong influence or
effect for example a boy who loves
history reads a lot of books on the
subject and researches to learn more to
have profound knowledge of history the
word profound is an adjective as it
describes something of being deep or
intense the word profoundly is an adverb
and it means totally or completely the
word profoundness is a noun okay now
